ked up 44 receiving yards.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.idahostatesman.com/sports/college/mountain-west/boise-state-university/boise-state-football/article184217246.html|title=Boise State\u2019s Mattison breaks school record, Harsin gets contract extension|publisher=Idaho Statesman|date=November 12, 2017|accessdate=November 13, 2017}}</ref>\n{{-}}\n\n===Air Force===\n{{See also|2017 Air Force Falcons football team}}\n{{AFB game box start\n|Title=Air Force at Boise State\n|Visitor=Falcons\n|Host='''No. 25 Broncos'''\n|V1=7|V2=3|V3=0|V4=9\n|H1=17|H2=10|H3=10|H4=7\n|Date=November 18, 2017\n|Location=[[Albertsons Stadium]]<br>[[Boise, Idaho|Boise, ID]]\n|TimeZone=MST\n|StartTime=8:26 p.m.\n|ElapsedTime=3 hours and 2 minutes\n|Attendance=33,030\n|Weather=Temperature: {{Convert|37|\u00b0F|\u00b0C}} \u2022 Weather: Fair \u2022 Wind: ESE 9\n|Referee=Reggie Smith\n|TVAnnouncers=Roy Philpott and [[Tom Ramsey]]\n|TVStation=[[ESPN2 College Football Saturday Primetime|ESPN2]]\n}}\n{{AFB game box end}}\n\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n{{CollegePrimaryHeader|team=Boise State Broncos|Overall record|Last meeting|Result}}\n|-\n|2\u20133\n|2016\n|AF, 27\u201320\n|}\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n|align=\"center\" Colspan=\"3\" |'''Uniform Combination'''\n|- align=\"center\"\n!style=\"{{CollegePrimaryStyle|Boise State Broncos|border=0|color=white}}\"|Helmet\n!style=\"{{CollegePrimaryStyle|Boise State Broncos|border=0|color=white}}\"|Jersey\n!style=\"{{CollegePrimaryStyle|Boise State Broncos|border=0|color=white}}\"|Pants\n|}\n\n* '''Passing leaders:''' Brett Rypien (BSU): 16\u201322, 300 YDS, 3 TD; Nate Romine (AF): 7\u201310, 115 YDS.\n* '''Rushing leaders:''' Alexander Mattison (BSU): 17 CAR, 42 YDS; Nate Romine (AF): 16 CAR, 54 YDS, 1 TD.\n* '''Receiving leaders:''' A.J. Richardson (BSU): 3 REC, 123 YDS, 1 TD; Marcus Bennett (AF): 3 REC, 63 YDS.\n{{-}}\n\n===at Fresno State===\n{{See also|2017 Fresno State Bulldogs football team|Boise State\u2013Fresno State foot