ite}}\"\n| '''Player''' || '''Position''' || '''Round''' || '''Pick''' || '''NFL Club''' \n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"\"\n| [[Leighton Vander Esch]] || LB || 1 || 19 ||  [[2018 Dallas Cowboys season|Dallas Cowboys]] \n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"\"\n| [[Cedrick Wilson Jr.]] || WR || 6 || 208 ||  [[2018 Dallas Cowboys season|Dallas Cowboys]] \n|}\n\n{{Clear}}\n\n==Personnel==\n===Coaching staff===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%;\"\n|-\n! Name \n! Position \n! Consecutive seasons at<br>Boise State in current position\n|-\n| [[Bryan Harsin]] || [[Head Coach]] ||align=center| 4th\n|-\n| Kent Riddle || Associate Head Coach, [[Tight End]]s, Special Teams Coordinator ||align=center| 4th, 3rd, 4th\n|-\n| Steve Caldwell || Assistant Head Coach, [[Defensive line coach|Defensive Line]] ||align=center| 4th, 4th\n|-\n| Zak Hill || [[Offensive Coordinator]], [[Quarterback]]s ||align=center| 2nd, 2nd\n|-\n| Andy Avalos || [[Defensive Coordinator]], [[Linebacker]]s ||align=center| 2nd, 4th\n|-\n| Lee Marks  || [[Running Back]]s ||align=center| 3rd\n|-\n| [[Eric Kiesau]] || [[Wide Receiver]]s ||align=center| 1st\n|-\n| [[Brad Bedell]] || [[Offensive line coach|Offensive Line]] ||align=center| 1st\n|-\n| [[Ashley Ambrose]] || [[Defensive Back]]s ||align=center| 2nd\n|-\n| Gabe Franklin || [[Safety (gridiron football position)|Safeties]] ||align=center| 2nd\n|-\n| Jeff Pitman  || Strength and Conditioning Coach || align=center| 3rd\n|-\n| colspan=\"4\"  style=\"font-size:8pt; text-align:center;\"|'''Reference:'''<ref name=CoachANDPlayers/>\n|}\n\n===Roster===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! No.\n! Name\n! Pos.\n! Ht.\n! Wt.\n! Cls.\n! Hometown (H.S./Prev. Exp.)\n|-\n| 1 || [[Cedrick Wilson Jr.]] || WR || 6-3 || 188 ||align=right| Sr. || [[Memphis, Tennessee|Memphis, TN]] ([[White Station High School|White Station HS]], [[Coffeyville Community College|Coffeyville CC]])\n|-\n| 3 || [[Montell Cozart]] || QB || 6-1 || 205 ||align=right| RS Sr. || [[Kansas City,